name: DESCENDANT X
description:
The life on planet Uhnon was wiped out by a sudden attack from an unknown entity, leaving only one survivor.
The last surviving Seephri tribe member wanders the infinite cosmos in search of something he doesn't understand.
He comes across a strange mass of soil, complete with vegetation and a serene atmosphere, after wandering the galaxy for who knows how many years, and he finally feels at peace.
He realised what he had been looking for for the first time: a sense of belonging. The feeling of Hands wrapped around him, a warm feeling.
